  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK591">
<l>uṭaimai yeṉappaṭuva tūkkamaḵ tillā </l>
<l>ruṭaiya tuṭaiyarō maṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Energy makes out the man of property; as for those who are destitute of it, do they (really) possess what they possess ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
